yse bietet neue Einblicke in evangelikales Leben und Missionieren in Deutschland und darüber hinaus.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 27. Jan 2023) 4aChristentum. 4aEthnografie. 4aEvangelikalismus. 4aJugend. 4aKultursoziologie. 4aMission. 4aMissionieren. 4aReligion. 4aReligionssoziologie. 4aReligionswissenschaft. 4aTeilnehmende Beobachtung. 4aTotalität. 4aTransnationalität. 7aRELIGION / General.2bisacsh  aChristianity.  aEthnography.  aEvangelicalism.  aMission.  aReligion.  aReligious Studies.  aSociology of Culture.  aSociology of Religion.  aTransnationality.  aYouth.08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Plus PP Package 2017 Part 2z978311076666008iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Plus eBook-Package 2017z978311071954308iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2017z9783110540550oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Social Sciences 2017z9783110548242oZDB-23-DSW0 cprintz978383763760140uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/9783839437605?locatt=mode:legacy40uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783839437605423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783839437605/original  a978-3-11-071954-3  DG Plus eBook-Package 2017b2017  a978-3-11-076666-0  DG Plus PP Package 2017 Part 2b2017  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_HICS  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_PPALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA5EBK  aZDB-23-DGGb2017  aZDB-23-DSWb2017